.
I purchased 100lbs of my favorite wax by @ezeecosmetics  After i filled up my wax pots, I stored the remainder of the wax (50lbs) in these plastic storage containers. 

These containers even have a scoop that attaches to the lid for easy refilling. As these containers start to go down over the next few weeks, i will refill them again with the remaining 50lbs.
